window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The devil paid me a visit and said I was going to one day rule his demonic kingdom.</b></p> <p>The catch: I have to attend the Infernal Academy, located in none other than Hell itself. Thankfully, I won’t be doing it alone. I’m going to surround myself with powerful demonesses (and maybe an angel or two as well).</p> <p>Come join me at the Infernal Academy, where the temperature is always warm, and the demonesses are hotter than a furnace.</p>"; 
